<D>__{switch hands.}
<C>__{alice}
<D>__{what?}
<C>__{julie}
<D>__{i'm serious. it was bicameral disjunction right brain and left brain out of balance. he was a rightie, so i made him switch the pencil to his left hand. just to see what'd come out.}
<A>__{a smile comes to julie's face. she settles in on the floor beside alice and digs through the various portfolios until she comes up with a quickie cartoon on the back of a napkin the prototype for...}
